data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the picturesque community of Emerson Park! This meticulously maintained 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence is an entertainer's delight. Situated on a giant corner lot, this property boasts two inviting porches, and a butterfly-friendly landscaped fenced-in backyard/garden, creating the perfect setting for gatherings.  The heart of the home is the gorgeous kitchen, featuring 42” cabinets,  an island with sink, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops – a true delight for any home chef. The well-designed floor plan makes this house ideal for families, with formal dining area, a guest bedroom, and a spacious family room on the first floor.     Upstairs, you'll find the 3 bedrooms and the oversized primary bedroom and bathroom. The master bathroom is a haven of relaxation, offering his/hers sinks, a jet tub, a stand-up shower, and a walk-in closet.    But the perks don't end there! This community offers a clubhouse featuring a theater room, playground, and a Junior Olympic-sized pool. No gym membership is needed, as access to the clubhouse gym is included with the dues. The fantastic location of this community ensures quick access to Downtown Orlando, Winter Garden, or Altamonte Springs via SR 414 or SR 429. It is minutes away from Wekiva State Park and Advent Health Hospital!    Don't miss out – schedule your viewing today!  SELLER TO PROVIDE CREDIT FOR CARPET ALLOWANCE
